'''Vinta Harvest Ale''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage brewed by [[Dug/Legends|Dugs]] and [[Vinta Corporation]] on [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare]]. The company that made it, of the same name as the beverage, was owned by [[Gran/Legends|Grans]], who hosted a [[Podracing/Legends|podracing]] circuit called the [[Vinta Harvest Classic/Legends|Vinta Harvest Classic]], which included the [[Phoebos Memorial Run/Legends|Phoebos Memorial Run]], the largest podracing course on Malastare.

==Behind the scenes==
[[File:BytDistombe-SW1998-14.jpg|thumb|right|150px|The label removed from the bottle by Marvel]]
When the digital version of [[Star Wars Omnibus: Emissaries and Assassins|''Omnibus: Emissaries and Assassins'']] was released in [[2015]] by [[Marvel Comics]], the label from the bottle was removed.

